Description:
Wellington Management Company is a private, independent investment management firm with client assets under management totaling over US$1 trillion.
The firm serves as investment advisor to over 2,150 institutions in over 60 countries, as of 30 December 2017. Its clients include central banks and sovereign institutions, pension funds, endowments and foundations, family offices, fund sponsors, insurance companies, financial intermediaries, and wealth managers.
